org.vertx.java.core.shareddata

Interface Shareable


  • public interface Shareable
    Marker interface. If a class implements this it means it can be put into shared data maps and sets. All classes that implement this MUST be threadsafe. Use this class with caution.
    Author:
    Tim Fox
